583ed788974f16197c678c","tid":1561950,"uid":284672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c3dfc0203f202a0ff8a067c60afa3920cfd641","tid":1561950,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"參觀Trump Tower"},{"pid":"25136eb736fb358ea3a7d2f20a5f2cbc4e3b4ef8","tid":1561950,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"睇黎我真係好黑，尋晚岩岩幫趁完forever 21，今日就執<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最快在本週日Forever21將宣布破產，受到銷量下滑、線上對手競爭激烈、消費者習慣改變，使得Forever21以實體店面銷售為主的營運模式大受衝擊。今年1-6月，其他業者在美國有超過7,000間零售店已關門，很多企業在2018年底購物季銷售狀況慘淡。Forever21在年輕消費者轉向線上購物之際仍持續拓展大型店面，這次Forever 21將關閉超過700間店，在此之前該公司已受到營運資金周轉問題，也已花費數個月尋找新的貸款。<br />\n2019年上半年，有14間零售業者包括至少20間店面宣布破產，包括Payless, Gymboree,Charlotte Russe Holdings, Charming Charlie, Barneys New York, A&rsquo;Gaci LLC&hellip;等。<br />\n1984年Forever 21成立，銷售低價服飾，公司決定關閉店面、減少店面空間、與房東協議降租，這波實體店面關店潮，受到Amazon的攻擊，大概超乎了市場預期，應該會持續一段時間。"},{"pid":"43d329ef73e3755d180ed5f484a564b18bc29098","tid":1561950,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"紐約有冇聲援香港集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5739fa342215fe29d0b1dd10a3e51b36c541ccd7","tid":1561950,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"唐人街早餐抵屌過香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZCzGyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZCzGyC.jpg&h=84c86227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebdd497491a6fa17e0984af77c02f32af8436772","tid":1561950,"uid":215443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5739fa342215fe29d0b1dd10a3e51b36c541ccd7","tid":1561